Oregon Oncology Specialists in Woodburn

Our office at Legacy Woodburn Health Center includes an infusion center and physician-supported care – Dr. Nick Barber and Britt Benn, PA-C see patients in Woodburn on Thursdays to provide you with follow-up care and treatments close to home. Sé habla Español.

Contact

Phone: 503-561-6444

Fax: 503-561-6440

Days of Operation: Thursday

After hours and during lunchtime, calls will be directed to our answering service. A provider is on call 24 hours a day, seven days a week.

Address

1475 Mount Hood Avenue

Suite 135

Woodburn, OR 97071

Get directions in Google Maps »

Visiting our Office

Creating a healthy and safe environment is important to us. If you are experiencing any cold or flu symptoms while visiting the clinic, we recommend the use of hand sanitizer and a mask to help protect others.

Physicians and APPs with offices at this location

Nicholas Barber, MD
